Text: Thank You Cc John Thanks for taking the time to meet with me on Wednesday afternoon Your synthesis of Enrons structured midmarket and trading deals visavis broad geographic classifications of electricity markets in North America was particularly enlightening I also appreciate your referring Dave Duran and Chris Calger of East and West Power Origination respectively Although I was unable to meet with Dave due to time constraints I expect to speak with him in the course of my discussions with Ben Jacobywho works with Dave Best regards Manuel
